  "sections": {
    "Description": "Alpha Scarabs are shaped like soft-shelled beetles. They attack similarly to artillery style Mech weapons. Alpha Scarabs will aim in a straight line at a tile and shoot over any tiles in between them and their target.",
    "Strategy": "Much like the standardScarab, the Alpha Scarab can usually be neutralized with one action by shoving it away from its target, due to its one-tile range. They do have more health points however, so in higher difficulties they will require more actions to take out."
  },
  "full_text": "Alpha Scarab\nDetails\nHealth\n4\nMove\n3\nSystems\nSpitting Glands\n(\nEnemy\n)\nEffect\nLob a powerful artillery shot at a single tile for 3 damage (5 tile range).\nAlpha Scarab\nis one of the Alpha\nVek\nfrom\nInto The Breach\n.\nDescription\n[\n]\nAlpha Scarabs are shaped like soft-shelled beetles. They attack similarly to artillery style Mech weapons. Alpha Scarabs will aim in a straight line at a tile and shoot over any tiles in between them and their target.\nStrategy\n[\n]\nMuch like the standard\nScarab\n, the Alpha Scarab can usually be neutralized with one action by shoving it away from its target, due to its one-tile range. They do have more health points however, so in higher difficulties they will require more actions to take out.\nv\n·\nd\n·\ne\nVek\nVek\nBeetle\n•\nBlobber\n•\nBurrower\n•\nCentipede\n•\nCrab\n•\nDigger\n•\nFirefly\n•\nHornet\n•\nLeaper\n•\nScarab\n•\nScorpion\n•\nSpider\n•\nVolatile Vek\nVek (Advanced Edition)\nBouncer\n•\nGastropod\n•\nMosquito\n•\nMoth\n•\nPlasmodia\n•\nStarfish\n•\nTumblebug\nAlpha Vek\nAlpha Beetle\n•\nAlpha Blobber\n•\nAlpha Burrower\n•\nAlpha Centipede\n•\nAlpha Crab\n•\nAlpha Digger\n•\nAlpha Firefly\n•\nAlpha Hornet\n•\nAlpha Leaper\n•\nAlpha Scarab\n•\nAlpha Scorpion\n•\nAlpha Spider\nAlpha Vek (Advanced Edition)\nAlpha Bouncer\n•\nAlpha Gastropod\n•\nAlpha Mosquito\n•\nAlpha Moth\n•\nAlpha Plasmodia\n•\nAlpha Starfish\n•\nAlpha Tumblebug\nVek Psions\nBlast Psion\n•\nBlood Psion\n•\nShell Psion\n•\nSoldier Psion\nVek Psions (Advanced Edition)\nArachnid Psion\n•\nRaging Psion\n•\nSmoldering Psion\nVek Minions\nBlob\n•\nAlpha Blob\n•\nSpiderling Egg\n•\nSpiderling\n•\nAlpha Spiderling\nVek Minions (Advanced Edition)\nSpore\n•\nAlpha Spore\n•\nVicious Spore\n•\nBlob Leader\nVek Leaders\nBeetle Leader\n•\nFirefly Leader\n•\nHornet Leader\n•\nLarge Goo\n(\nMedium Goo\n) (\nSmall Goo\n) •\nPsion Abomination\n•\nScorpion Leader\n•\nSpider Leader\nVek Leaders (Advanced Edition)\nBlobber Leader\n•\nBo